channel.title: Project fnatic - all or nothing
channel.description:
[IMG]http://i429.photobucket.com/albums/qq20/nathanz1_2008/cooltext795778523.png[/img]
Project fnatic is a new project created and thought of by yours truly. I aim to obtain the "perfect server".. not because of the perfectness but because of the nature and amusement and of course amazement.. the reason why this project is called "fnatic" is because of the term "fanatic" which means " a person whose enthusiasm or zeal for something is extreme or beyond normal limits " it will be a server built entirely out of motivation and thrill.. this is basically a blank p.i, but once i'm finished it will look nothing like one. I basically aim to make one of the most professional 474 p.i's ever made. My last project "last chapter" got shut down due to my "buddy" stealing the donations and shutting the vps off. If you would like to join in on the project please pm me letting me know what experience you have and what roll you wish to fill.
[IMG]http://i429.photobucket.com/albums/qq20/nathanz1_2008/ownercrown.png[/img]: Nathan [IMG]http://i429.photobucket.com/albums/qq20/nathanz1_2008/Admin-Crown.gif[/img]: Haven't decided. [img]http://www.upload.ee/image/2763845/forum_image.png[/img]:[URL=http://"www.project-fnatic.net"]Forums[/URL]
